<footer class="border-t border-outline bg-surface-alt">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-on-surface-heading font-bold text-xl tracking-tight">
          <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-grad-from via-grad-via to-grad-to text-white text-sm font-black">L</span>
          Luminary Films
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-md text-on-surface-muted leading-relaxed">
          We believe every brand has a story worth telling — beautifully.
          Based in Los Angeles, working worldwide.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4">
          <a href="#" class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-outline text-on-surface-muted hover:text-primary hover:border-primary transition-colors" aria-label="Instagram">
